http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/EoI-sought-for-master-plan/article14021149.ece

A master plan will be prepared to for improving facilities in the zoo. The Project Implementation Unit in the Forest Department has sought expression of interest from renowned consultants to prepare the Master Plan.The last date for submission of bids has been extended to February 10 from January 20.The consultant is supposed to prepare Master Plan for redevelopment, defining the vision and functional aspects with reference to existing structures, site conditions, area available, existing resources, animal population, animal health care, financial sustainability, conservation education and visitor experiences.The consultant will be mandates to define different phases of implementation, carry out survey, investigation, stakeholder consultations, inventory/resource base and development options.